docs {
  # Replace Vendor

  Completely replaces a vendor. All fields must be provided (except `id` which is preserved from the URL).

  ## Path Parameters

  | Param | Description |
  |-------|-------------|
  | id | Vendor identifier |

  ## Request Body

  ```json
  {
    "name": "NVIDIA Corporation",
    "description": "Leading GPU and AI computing company",
    "website": "https://nvidia.com"
  }
  ```

  ## Response

  Returns the replaced vendor object with status `200 OK`.

  ## Error Responses

  - `404 Not Found`: Vendor does not exist
  - `400 Bad Request`: Invalid JSON body
}
